snippet.title: The Mortuary Assistant: Definitive Edition - Out Now!
snippet.description:
The Mortuary Assistant: Definitive Edition is finally here! New bodies, new haunt events, embalming only mode, and more along with bug and stability fixes is here on all consoles and Steam!

*Get it on Steam*
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1295920/The_Mortuary_Assistant/
*Get it on PlayStation*
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10006285
*Get it on Switch*
https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/the-mortuary-assistant-switch/

The Developer: https://x.com/DSDigitalDev
DreadXP: https://x.com/DreadXPGames
